The description says:

I decided to recreate the fighting music used in one of my favorite Regular Show episodes: Exit 9B! I made this using Sytrus, and cheap soundfonts! :D

Hope you enjoy it! Maybe someday, the original track will be released, and I'll never cry again.

P.S. Sorry for the long pause of silence in the end. Sometimes FL Studio does that when rendering, usually towards release-y instruments.
